            "description": "Research Topic: Data analysis from the beam test at DESY of the FOCAL prototype calorimeter for ALICE group at CERN. In this project, by analysing data obtained from the beam test at DESY accelerator, I studied the behaviour of the digital e/m prototype calorimeter as well as the longitudinal and lateral profiles to investigate its energy resolution and Moliere radius for comparison with the theoretical expected values. Lab experience obtained: Member of the Utrecht group in several beam tests for FOCAL prototype at LHC accelerator (Geneva, Switzerland) and DESY accelerator (Hamburg, Germany).\n",
